**
E-01 CANCL OR A CHG WAS APPOINTED, BUT PROC M/F DOESN'T EXST
E-02 PROCESS M/F INPUT OVER 15  PROCESSES
E-03 PROCESS CODE IS INPUT, AND SECTION CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-04 PROCESS CODE IS NOT INPUT  ONLY SECTION CODE IS INPUT
E-05 PROCESS CODE IS INPUT, AND LOCATION IS NOT INPUT
E-06 PROCESS CODE IS NOT INPUT, AND LOCATION IS INPUT
E-07 PROCESS NO APPOINTED IS TOO BIG
E-08 WHEN IT'S CHILD P/N, IT DOESN'T CHG BEFORE REVERS PROC
E-09 IT CAN NOT CANCEL OVER 2 PROCESSES
E-10 THE PROCESS CODE WHICH THERE IS NOT  PROCESS NAME M/F
E-11 ALL ITEM OF ADD PROCESS IS NOT INPUT
E-12 THERE IS NOT PROCESS CODE OF ADD IN PROCESS NAME M/F
E-13 KANBAN CHANGE DATE(FIRST 6 COLUMNS)IS LOGICAL ERROR
E-14 KANBAN CHANGE DATE BIN(LAST 2 COLUMNS) IS LOGIC ERROR
E-15 PROCESS CODE INPUT REPEATEDLY
E-16 RETURN TO NEXT PROC P/N BY KEY P/N COMBINATION
E-17 THERE ISN'T OVER 15 PROC THAT INQ PROC NO OF CHILD P/N
E-18 APPOINT LAST TIME ERR CHG INST 13.(USUAL=. ,CHG=*)
E-19 THERE ISN'T THE SECTION WILL INPUT IN DETAILS M/F
E-20 IT IS ACCEPTED CMD-2 WITH CHANGE SCREEN OF KEY P/N
E-21 IT ISN'T ACCEPTED CMD-3 WITH CHG SCREEN OF KEY P/N
E-22 THERE ISN'T PROC NO APPOINTED INQ PROC NO OF CHILD P/N
E-23 IT ISN'T ACCEPTED CMD- 9 WITH CHANGE SCREEN OF KEY P/N
E-24 PROCESS IS NEVER INPUT
E-25 PROCESS IS INPUT, BUT CAN NOT PICK UP KEY P/N
E-26 THOUGH PROCESS IS NOT INPUT, PROCESS KEY P/N IS INPUT
E-27 K CHG DATE IS SMALL OR EQUAL TO  A DATE BEFORE CHANGE
E-28THERE IS NO INTRA-PROCESS LOCATION WHICH CAN USE
E-29 IT IS DIFFERENT FROM K KIND OF INTRA-PROC LOC M/F
E-30 KANBAN CHANGE M/F AND PROCESS M/F IS DIFFERENT
E-31 NEXT PROC THAT K CHG DATE ISN'T CHANGED
E-32 BECAUSE IT ISN'T TUNNEL LOC, K KIND HAS TO INPUT
E-33 CHANGE DATE IS SMALLER THAN  OPEN LOC DATE IN LOC M/F
E-34 KANBAN CHANGE DATE IS NOT INPUT
E-35 THOUGH IT IS TUNNEL PROCESS, KANBAN KIND IS INPUT
E-36 IMPOSSIBLE TO ADD PROC AT CHG SCREEN FOR RELETIVE C-P/N
E-37 IMPOSSIBLE TO CHG DATE AT CHG SCREEN FOR RELETIVE C-P/N
E-38 PROCESS WAS CHANGED, BUT K CHG DATE ISN'T CHANGED
     LOC OF PROC ISN'T INPUT IN INTRA-PROC LOC M/F
     IT'S DIFFERENT FROM LOC M/F IN K KIND OF PROC
E-41 BACK THE VALUE BEFORE. PROC NO MUSTN'T CHG BEFORE ENTER
E-42 COMMON P/N IS + AT THIS PROC NO. NOT CHG TO TUNNEL LOC
E-43 NEXT PROC K CHG DATE OF THE PROC CHANGED IS SMALL
E-44 PROC NO THAT IT WAS APPOINTED IS INPUT BY A MINUS VALUE
